  <h1 class="uswds-page-title page-title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">Two patient’s stomachs kept “alive” after removal in novel study to understand stomach cancer</span>
</h1>


  </div>
<div id="block-addtoanybuttons" class="block block-addtoany block-addtoany-block">
  
    
